4... Bxb4 5. c3
{ This is the move that earns the extra tempo for us, now we can get d2-d4 in very quickly. }
5... Ba5
{ This is Black's best response. The idea is that in the case of d2-d4 the c3-pawn is pinned and so White can't achieve their dream center setup. }
6. d4
