1. e4 c5 2. c3 Nf6 3. e5 Nd5 4. Nf3 Nc6 5. d4 cxd4 6. Bc4 e6 7. cxd4 d6 8. O-O
Be7 9. Qe2 O-O 10. Re1 dxe5 11. dxe5 b6 12. Nc3 Nxc3 13. bxc3 Bb7 14. Bd3 Na5
