{ White finishes development with this natural move. The general goal upon completing development is to try to trade down to an endgame where the queenside pawn majority can become a decisive factor. }
10... Nd7 11. O-O
{ 11.O-O-O  was tested between Duda and Carlsen but here Black seems to have plenty of play after the thematic  11...b5! }
